        <p class="text-neutral-600">Bupa Global or Cigna Global—premium service, worldwide coverage, no annual limits. These insurers are familiar with high-net-worth clients and provide concierge-style service. Budget HK$6,000-10,000/month for comprehensive individual coverage.</p>
