      <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Entrepreneur/Business Owner</h4>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">AXA Hong Kong or Allianz Care—good balance of coverage and cost. Local insurers have strong hospital networks; international insurers add global coverage for business travel. Budget HK$2,000-5,000/month.</p>
