    <p class="mb-4">
      Hong Kong is one of the world's most expensive cities. The CIES requires HK$30 million investment; the Investment Visa has no fixed minimum but requires realistic business funding. Living costs, especially housing, are extremely high.
    </p>

    <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">Total Cost Estimates</h3>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">CIES (Passive Investment)</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
