        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">Rejected. Immigration found: insufficient capital for F&B setup, no relevant experience, generic business plan without Hong Kong specifics, no clear competitive advantage. Advised to demonstrate industry experience and realistic funding. Lesson: HK values business viability and your ability to execute.</p>
